## Severity Classification

| Severity | Description | Target Resolution |
| -------- | ----------- | ----------------- |
| Critical | Active exploitation possible | 24-48 hours |
| High | Significant risk, no active exploit | 7 days |
| Medium | Limited risk | 30 days |
| Low | Minimal risk | Next release |

